pe=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"419\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/2025-Art-Market-APPLICATION-Header-1024x536.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-13347\" alt=\"Art Market at the Wisconsin Arts and Peony Festival Beaver Dam Wisconsin\" srcset=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/2025-Art-Market-APPLICATION-Header-1024x536.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/2025-Art-Market-APPLICATION-Header-300x157.jpg 300w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/2025-Art-Market-APPLICATION-Header-768x402.jpg 768w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/2025-Art-Market-APPLICATION-Header-1536x804.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/2025-Art-Market-APPLICATION-Header.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b2c49da elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b2c49da\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Seeking Artists for the \nWI Arts &amp; Peony Festival<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d900fe4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d900fe4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Every year on the second weekend of June the Wisconsin Arts &amp; Peony Festival hosts an Art Market in Downtown Beaver Dam. The year 2026 is the 6th year for this annual festival and we are looking for Wisconsin art vendors that focus on painting, ceramics, woodworks, metal works, jewelry, fiber arts, glass works, and mixed media (and more)! Artists are chosen using a juried process and chosen by committee.\u00a0<\/p><p>Last year&#8217;s Wisconsin Arts and Peony Festival brought in nearly 11K visitors!\u00a0<\/p><p>This year we expect to have 100 art vendors and encourage you to fill out an application. Click <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/beeid.org\/0907b79f63bd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HERE<\/a><\/strong> for an application and more information about the Art Market.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-5c4302c\" data-id=\"5c4302c\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-db38316 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"db38316\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/AdobeStock_347429377-1024x576.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-9070\" alt=\"Food Truck Vendor\" srcset=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/AdobeStock_347429377-1024x576.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/AdobeStock_347429377-300x169.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/AdobeStock_347429377-768x432.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/AdobeStock_347429377-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/AdobeStock_347429377-2048x1152.jpeg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-deb261b elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"deb261b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Food Trucks &amp; Good Eats Wanted! <\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c6c5d44 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c6c5d44\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The Beaver Dam Chamber &amp; Visitor Center hosts and organizes many events throughout the year. Food trucks are a great way to provide a variety of different cuisine to our participants and attendees.<\/p><p>Below is a summary of 2026 events that are both free and with a fee.<\/p><p>June 12-14 | <a href=\"https:\/\/visitbeaverdam.com\/wisconsin-arts-peony-festival-beaver-dam-wi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Wisconsin Arts and Peony Festival &amp; Art Market<\/a><br \/>June 20 | <a href=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/taste-of-wisconsin\/\">18th Annual Taste of Wisconsin<\/a> (Beer and Cheese Festival)<br \/>July | Movie Under the Stars (outdoor movie)<br \/>August | Movie Under the Stars (outdoor movie)<br \/>September 18 | <a href=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/community-events\/wine-tour\/\">Wine Tour<\/a><br \/>October 31 | <a href=\"https:\/\/visitbeaverdam.com\/fall-downtown-fest-casket-races\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Fall Downtown Fest<\/a><\/p><p>Click <a href=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/community-events\/#id=1654&amp;cid=1829&amp;wid=701\" target=\"_bl